overview: EVOLVE 68 was an event put on by Evolve. It took place on September 10, 2016 at the NYWC Sportatorium in Long Island,  Fred Yehi vs Jigsaw  Ethan Page vs. Dan Barry  TJ Perkins vs. Darby Allin  Tracy Williams vs DUSTIN (Extreme Rules Match)  Tony Nese vs Matt Riddle vs Ricochet  Drew Galloway vs. Drew Gulak  Zack Sabre Jr. vs. Johnny Gargano
title: EVOLVE 68
